original: Larsson, Lars Erik, jordbrukskonsulent, Linköping, f. 30/8/85 i Norra Fågelås, Skarab. 1., av lantbr. Johan L. o. Axelina Andersson. G. 25 m. Märta Edling. Barn: Inger f. 27, Carin 31. — Agronomex. å Alnarp 17, jordbr:stud. i Tyskl. 15. Tf. jordbr:-konsulent i Gävleb. län 18-19, ord. dito i östergötl. län sed. 20.
translated: Larsson, Lars Erik, agricultural consultant, Linköping, b. 30/8/85 in Norra Fågelås, Skarab. 1st, son of farmer Johan L. and Axelina Andersson. Married on 25th to Märta Edling. Children: Inger b. 27, Carin b. 31. — Graduated from Alnarp Agricultural College in 1917, studied agriculture in Germany in 1915. Acting agricultural consultant in Gävleborg County from 1918-1919, regular in Östergötland County since 1920.
